What is EC2 autoscaling group?
Ec2 Autoscaling nothing but add or remove EC2 instances automatically

or

EC2 autoscaling nothing but that automatically adust the number of EC2 instances in your infrastructure based on demand, means 
add or remove instances automatically.
it ensures high availability, cost optimization of application.

Core concept:
-------------
-Traffic ----> instances automatically increases
-Traffic -----> instances automatically decreases
-Failes instance ----> automatically replaced

Components:
-----------
1. Launch template:
Defines how instances are created:
Includes:
-AMI (OS image) 
-EBS (Block storage)
-Networking
-Security groups
-key pair

2.Group Size:
AGS is the backbone it defines:
-Minimum instances size : 1
-Desired instances size : 4
-Maximum instances size : 500


